Data for NestWatch Workflow Examples

Source: R/wren-quickstart.R
wren_quickstart.Rd

Data from the NestWatch database (V2), subset to include all nesting data for Carolina ("carwre") and Bewick's ("bewwre") wrens. These are un-cleaned and un-filtered from the database.

Usage

wren_quickstart

Format

A dataframe with 40290 observations of 54 variables. See <https://doi.org/10.1002/ecy.4230> for details of variables.
